f:\mathbb{Z}\times\mathbb{Z}\to \mathbb{R}
x\mapsto f(x,a)
x\mapsto f(a,x)
\le N
f
P(x, y)
A\subset\mathbb{Z}
|A|=N+1
A=\{0,1,\ldots,N\}
P(x,y)=\sum_{(m,n)\in A\times A}\left(f(m,n)\prod\limits_{s\in A-\{m\}}\frac{(x-s)}{(m-s)}\prod\limits_{t\in A-\{n\}}\frac{(y-t)}{(n-t)}\right)
P(x,y)=f(x,y)
(x,y)\in \mathbb{Z}\times\mathbb{Z}
(x,y)\in A\times A
